0.0.1.name: wordpress/cawaii-admin
0.0.1.description: This plugin enables you to look the WordPress admin panel cawaii. You can choose where to locate the menu, how the background looks, and change the color of links, boxes and so on. You can also change Logos of the admin panel and login page, you can choose which metaboxes to remove from dashboard and post-new pages.
